          </Paragraph>
        </Article>
      </Chapter>
      <Chapter Num="4">
        <ChapterTitle>第四章　衝撃試験機</ChapterTitle>
        <Article Num="24">
          <ArticleTitle>第二十四条</ArticleTitle>
          <Paragraph Num="1">
            <ParagraphNum/>
            <ParagraphSentence>
              <Sentence>衝撃試験機ノ振子系ノ吊心及重心並ニ衝撃刃縁ノ中点ハ一直線上ニ在ルコトヲ要ス</Sentence>
            </ParagraphSentence>
          </Paragraph>
        </Article>
        <Article Num="25">
          <ArticleTitle>第二十五条</ArticleTitle>
          <Paragraph Num="1">
            <ParagraphNum/>
            <ParagraphSentence>
              <Sentence>衝撃試験機ノ衝撃刃縁ノ中点ト撃心トハ能フ限リ一致セシムルコトヲ要シ其ノ距離ハ一〇ミリメートルヲ超エザルヲ標準トス</Sentence>
            </ParagraphSentence>
          </Paragraph>
        </Article>
        <Article Num="26">
          <ArticleTitle>第二十六条</ArticleTitle>
          <Paragraph Num="1">
            <ParagraphNum/>
            <ParagraphSentence>
              <Sentence>衝撃試験機ノ鎚ノ最大振上リ角度ハ持上ゲ角度ヨリ小ニシテ其ノ差ハ一度ヲ超ユルコトヲ得ズ</Sentence>
            </ParagraphSentence>
          </Paragraph>
        </Article>
      </Chapter>
